#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Note" field of the "Patron" table</h2>
This field contains multiple lines to give the driver more information
about how to deliver to the patron.  It may include information such
as that they need to be called first, which door to deliver, that they
are hard of hearing, or that they are younger that you might be
expecting.

